txt.en: Thank you for contributing your collection! Please place your items in the box to receive your reward.
Wanted: Dusky ears from beasts near Amon Raith. Deliver the items to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith.
'These look much the same, and I am sure there will be no way to tell the difference. Thank you.'
'Agnes must really hate bears. She said that she wants only bear ears, but I wager she cannot tell them apart.'
DNT HIDING CONTENT - Task: Dusky Ears
Nathan Hodges, at Amon Raith, awaits the collection and delivery of dusky ears.
Deliver the dusky ears to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith
Wanted: Dusky ears from beasts near Amon Raith.
